# sdg3-University Health Clinic Appointment System
this is a prototype supporting SDG 3 : good health and well being

Project Title - University Health Clinic Appointment System

SDG Chosen - SDG 3 (Project Description)
SDG 3 focuses on imrpoving the health and wellbeing of students these studentes might often wait long hours in clinics hence this system can help them booking appointments online and free of cost.
- appointment booking
- select available doctors or preffered ones.
- choose time slots

